He's speaking like he's berating a bunch of schoolchildren too stupid or ignorant to know what's best for them.  That's almost even more insulting than what Bush said about North Korea.  After all, you can rest assured that Kim Jong Il and the rest of them know exactly what sort of an operation they're running, and how the West sees them.<br>
